# DI and Routing Checklist

When creating or changing a feature, ensure all of the following:

- Add route name constant in `core/navigation/app_route_names.dart`.
- Add route entry in `core/navigation/router_provider.dart`.
- For detail/edit routes, pass route IDs via provider overrides.
- Register in `lib/di.dart` using `registerFeatureStack`:
  - `name` must end with `DataSource` (e.g. `CoffeesDataSource` → `CoffeesDataSourceRemote` / `CoffeesDataSourceLocal`).
  - `createRepository: FeatureRepository.builder`
- Register each use case: `locator.registerLazySingleton(() => MyUsecase(locator()));`
- Do not leave a feature partially wired (files exist but route/DI missing).

# Completion Rule

- Before finishing, verify: navigation → controller → `runUseCase` → use case → repository → data source.
